      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Daily wage = Total payment / Days worked\n\nPiece rate = Payment per unit produced\nTotal pay = Units × Rate per unit\n\nContractor pay:\n  Total cost = Σ(workers × rate × days)",
