      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Overtime rate = Normal rate × multiplier\nCommon: 1.5× or 2× normal rate\n\nTotal pay = (Normal hrs × Normal rate)\n          + (OT hrs × OT rate)\n\nIf daily wage given:\n  Hourly rate = Daily wage / Normal hrs",
