      "x": 1005,
      "y": 545,
      "width": 801,
      "height": 65,
      "text": "A can do a piece of work in 20 days. He works for 8 days\nand leaves. B finishes the remaining work in 9 days. If\nthe total contract amount is Rs.4000, how much should B\nget?",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
