      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 931,
      "width": 773,
      "height": 33,
      "text": "15 men can complete a work in 12 days and are paid\nRs.54000 in total. What is the daily wage of each man?",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
