    {
      "id": "el_45",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1012,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Men: 5x600x8 = Rs.24,000\nStep 2: Women: 4x400x8 = Rs.12,800\nStep 3: Total = 24000+12800 = Rs.36,800\n\nTRICK:\nTotal = sum(workers x rate x days)\nEfficiency info is irrelevant here!\nWages = actual persons x their rate\n= (5x600 + 4x400) x 8 = Rs.36,800\n\nAnswer: Rs.36,800 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
